Harry R. COLEMAN, Petitioner, v. DISTRICT COURT OF THE UNITED STATES FOR THE DISTRICT OF OREGON et al., Respondents. No. 6202. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Sept. 18, 1930.

Before DIETRICH and WILBUR, Circuit Judges, and WEBSTER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

It appearing that the cause against petitioner has been set down for early hearing, the petition is dismissed.
